  ██    The show returns for the much-anticipated second series. One    ██   ██
  ██  talented fashion designer will get the opportunity of a lifetime  ██   ██
  ██ to launch their career in the world of Australian fashion. The six ██   ██
  ██     previously eliminated designers return to team up with the     ██   ██
  ██ remaining six designers to create an outfit and head piece for the ██   ██
  ██ Spring Carnival. Alex Zabotto-Bentley returns as guest judge and,  ██   ██
  ██ along with Kristy and the panel, puts the heat under the remaining ██   ██
  ██                             designers.                             ██   ██
